import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='delay', kde=True, color='blue')
    median_delay = data['delay'].median()
    plt.axvline(median_delay, color='red', linestyle='--', label=f'Median: {median_delay:.2f}')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of flight delays?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Delay (minutes)')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.boxplot(data=data, y='distance')
    avg_distance = data['distance'].mean()
    plt.axhline(avg_distance, color='r', linestyle='--', label=f'Average Distance: {avg_distance:.2f}')
    plt.title('What is the average distance of flights?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    origin_counts = data['origin'].value_counts().reset_index()
    destination_counts = data['destination'].value_counts().reset_index()
    origin_counts.columns = ['airport', 'count']
    destination_counts.columns = ['airport', 'count']
    combined_counts = pd.concat([origin_counts, destination_counts])
    combined_counts = combined_counts.groupby('airport').sum().reset_index()
    combined_counts = combined_counts.sort_values('count', ascending=False)

    plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
    sns.barplot(x='airport', y='count', data=combined_counts, palette='viridis')
    plt.title('What is the most common origin and destination for flights?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Airport')
    plt.ylabel('Number of Flights')
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)

    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]

    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.scatterplot(data=data, x='distance', y='delay', hue='origin', palette='viridis')
    plt.title('What is the relationship between delay time and distance?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Distance')
    plt.ylabel('Delay')
    plt.legend(title='Origin', loc='upper right')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
